          "message": "The SQL filter `AND (${orgId}::bigint IS NULL OR t.\"id\" = ${orgId} OR t.\"parentId\" = ${orgId})` in getTeamsWithPBACPermissions incorrectly treats orgId as a team parentId, which may return teams whose parentId matches the orgId rather than teams belonging to the organization. This can cause incorrect permission resolution when orgId is provided.",
          "suggestion": "Verify the intended semantics: if orgId refers to an organization (Team with parentId IS NULL), the filter should check t.\"parentId\" = ${orgId} for child teams, but the direct t.\"id\" = ${orgId} check may match the org team itself, which is likely not intended. Consider using a separate organization membership table or a dedicated orgId column.",
