          "severity": "high",
          "category": "bug_risk",
          "message": "The SQL filter `AND (${orgId}::bigint IS NULL OR org.\"id\" = ${orgId} OR child.\"id\" = ${orgId})` in the UNION query of getTeamsWithPBACPermissions may incorrectly include the organization team itself (org.id = orgId) when only child teams should be returned. This can lead to granting permissions to the org team itself, which may be unintended.",
          "suggestion": "Review the intended behavior: if orgId represents an organization, the filter should likely be `child.\"parentId\" = ${orgId}` instead of `org.\"id\" = ${orgId} OR child.\"id\" = ${orgId}`. Clarify the data model and adjust the SQL accordingly.",
